{
  "info": {
    "name": "Raizes do Nordeste API",
    "description": "Colecao de testes da API Raizes do Nordeste. Projeto multidisciplinar UNINTER, trilha Back-End, 2026.\n\nAntes de rodar:\n1. Sobe a API com `uvicorn main:app --reload`\n2. Roda `python seed.py` se ainda nao rodou\n3. Roda a colecao em ordem (T01 -> T16)\n\nOs tokens (adminToken, clienteToken) e o pedidoId sao capturados automaticamente pelos scripts de teste.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminToken",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "clienteToken",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "pedidoId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "pedidoIdRecusa",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Autenticacao",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "T01 - Login admin (200)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "var data = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Tem access_token', function () { pm.expect(data.access_token).to.be.a('string'); });",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', data.access_token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@raizes.com\",\n  \"senha\": \"Admin@123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "T02 - Login cliente (200)",
          "event": [
